snippet: Drive Space Indicator helps you stay on top of available disk space by doing the following: it changes the icons you see in Computer (or My Computer) and puts a progress bar under each icon; the pr...
content: Drive Space Indicator helps you stay on top of available disk space by doing the following: it changes the icons you see in Computer (or My Computer) and puts a progress bar under each icon; the progress bar displays how full your drives are.
